Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3948] added 
``help --find``
 to search usage and extra_usage text for strings
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3923] allowed fetch to follow redirects
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3939] allowed 
``source``
 to accept paths with emojis
filaretov update to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3936] only allow unaliasing in current scope, add tests
jt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3935] bumped rustyline and added unalias test
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3924] switched back to building for size
epost 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3922] fixed 'Inimplemented' typo.
knottio 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3921] added trailing slash in completion of symlinked dir
andrasio created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3919] the zip command.
elferherrera created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3918] PROMPT_STRING env variable
soumil-07 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3879] added the ability to remove and list aliases
